{"tid":83000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗中年文員拳打撐警大聯盟成員背部判囚　上訴遭駁回","createTime":"2017-01-16T11:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T13:31:09.000Z","uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e424096ae700fca1b4504a4826597384e391f9e","tid":83000,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/318434-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E8%83%8C%E9%83%A8%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A+%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F318434-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2583%258C%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%2B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E&d=SYfG%2FrpWfShsoGytOeV0sUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=26e28a86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F318434-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2583%258C%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%2B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E&h=db23c52f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/318434-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E8%83%8C%E9%83%A8%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A+%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E</a><br />\n撐警大聯盟成員在2015年2月在大埔墟火車站外擺街站時，與本土派及熱血公民衝突，期間中年文員戴錦山（三十九歲）拳打一名撐警義工的背部3至4下，經審訊後被裁定普通襲擊罪成，判囚十四天。戴不服定罪及判刑，早前向高院提出上訴。法官今宣佈判決，駁回其上訴申請，戴的保釋即時被撤銷，上訴人須開始服刑。<br />\n上訴人指，裁判官在原審時忽略了控辯雙方證人的證供有重大分歧，錯誤地認為辯方證人對當時情況的觀察不準確；又指裁判官判處監禁刑罰是明顯過重或原則上錯誤。<br />\n法官在判決書中表示，同意裁判官所指兩名控方證人之證供分歧只屬事件中的細微枝節，而因辯方證人在事主被圍毆時的觀察並不全面，才較為依賴控方證人之證供的看法，故認為原審裁判官的分析並無不合理。法官又認同裁判官視本案為嚴重性質的普通襲擊罪行，故認為14天即時監禁不屬明顯過重，遂駁回戴的定罪及刑事上訴。"},{"pid":"ac36a9da11257158cb869fe913a21881ea93baeb","tid":83000,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"39歲(熱血)"},{"pid":"98e12fe22568fcff84ce846c2a5642a429440083","tid":83000,"uid":20659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494208f428eea2aab9ce3c0a62e2dca309db8df7","tid":83000,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2454111944e9d79481818af3c3ae758288f80cf","tid":83000,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話我地熱血手足唔勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f26ae2b6c2a3bd7553150e4445bba7ebb382cbb","tid":83000,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"選擇性判刑為支那服務<br />\n香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec2ae184b080aa670c753d56c1cee38c9636a7f","tid":83000,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"如果打同被打嗰個調返轉會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcbc8017e2